  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The universe recognized you with its eyeless eyes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you wake up from your doze, you find yourself in an uninhabited station. In this short horror-adventure, you must escape and survive from the “She”, monster in a dead body bag that rules the strange subway station.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About this game</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is controlled by keyboard and mouse.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore every nook and cranny of the subway station to find your way forward.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no way for humans to stand up to the “She”.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The universe recognized you with its eyeless eyes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you wake up from your doze, you find yourself in an uninhabited station. In this short horror-adventure, you must escape and survive from the “She”, monster in a dead body bag that rules the strange subway station.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About this game</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is controlled by keyboard and mouse.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore every nook and cranny of the subway station to find your way forward.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no way for humans to stand up to the “She”.</p></li></ul>",
